    <item>
      <title>美国就业报告缓解经济增长担忧，欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/european-stocks-edge-higher-as-investors-await-us-job-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五上涨，此前一份意外强劲的美国就业报告鼓舞了投资者，使他们相信经济状况良好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/european-stocks-edge-higher-as-investors-await-us-job-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 07:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新思考美联储路径，股市和收益率上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就业报告强于预期，迫使交易员们对美联储下次降息幅度的押注有所收敛，美国国债价格下跌。数据凸显了美国经济的韧性，并提振了软着陆的希望，股市继续小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
